frobenius-norm   ( m -- f )               √(Σ aᵢⱼ²) over all elements (same value as norm)
norm             ( m -- f )               Euclidean (L2) norm: √(Σ aᵢⱼ²) over all elements — a vector's length; for a matrix the Frobenius (entrywise 2-)norm, not the spectral norm
